</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/5" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>NAME OF TALE</strong> The &quot;Existential Maw of Despair&quot; National Park!<br />
<strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721490" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;">Tufto</a></span>. This tale is part of the <a href="/end-of-death-hub">End of Death</a> canon, and forms the first part of a tale series, &quot;Lookout 281&quot;. More of Tufto's work can be found <a href="/tufto-personnel-file">here</a>.</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
<div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">rating:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+48</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="I like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="I don't like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="Cancel my vote" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
</div>
</div>
